reviewText: I would love to buy a copy of this show! Saw it years ago and really liked it.
This was one of my favorite movies growing up.  I've been looking for this for years.

A funny movie with a very talented cast (Bob Hope, Eve St. Marie, George Sands, Pearl Bailey). Why has this movie not been released in a dvd format? I, too, have been looking for years to purchase a copy.
I love this movie and have been looking for it for a few years now.  Sure hope more DVD copies are made.
